                   <p>We are experienced in handling cases involving will and trust disputes and have been retained by multiple attorneys for these complex issues. Our team is experienced in probate litigation, power of attorney documentation, guardianship, conservatorship, health care proxy documentation, trusts, real estate and other fiduciary services.</p>
