              <div class="service-description">
                <p>We understand that patient care is often improved by swift action at the courthouse. We have 20+ years experience providing patient care services and the relationships throughout the Commonwealth to facilitate expeditious processing of patient care cases. Whether an emergency hearing is required for swift patient treatment or you are looking for assistance in providing legal services to your employees at a health care organization, we can provide you with the services you need.</p>
                <p><%= link_to "Learn more...", health_care_providers_practices_path, :class => "service-learn-more" %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </p>
          <p>
            <div class="service-group-summary">
              <a href="javascript:void(0);">Families</a>
              <div class="service-description">
                <p>At Ready, Beaulieu, Saunders & Kostin LLP, we have families too. Like you, we want to protect our loved ones, improve our lives and perhaps try to leave something for the next generation. While the typical family does not need to have a lawyer on retainer, all families should consult with an attorney regarding several very important issues. We recommend that every adult consult a legal professional in key areas including Estate Planning, Real Estate Transactions and Preventative Steps to Protect Your Family.</p>
                <p><%= link_to "Learn more...", families_practices_path, :class => "service-learn-more" %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </p>
          <p>
            <div class="service-group-summary">
              <a href="javascript:void(0);">New Adults</a>
              <div class="service-description">
                <p>As a new adult you are now able to make some serious decisions. Being a grown-up can come with new rights as well as many new responsibilities. With these rights, it is now possible for you set your own rules for control of your health care treatment, finances and other relationships with individuals and organizations through contractual documents. Working with our firm can ensure that your rights are protected and that your interests are served.</p>
                <p><%= link_to "Learn more...", new_adults_practices_path, :class => "service-learn-more" %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </p>
          <p>
