              <a href="javascript:void(0);">Seniors</a>
              <div class="service-description">
                <p>At Ready, Beaulieu, Saunders & Kostin LLP we are committed to serving seniors in our community.  We understand that at this stage in life there can be many questions and concerns. Estate planning and gifting, real estate services and elder protective services are areas where we may be able to help you. We are also here to answer any general questions you may have about your life, health or property.</p>
                <p><%= link_to "Learn more...", seniors_practices_path, :class => "service-learn-more" %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </p>
